No.

1016
01:30:21,001 --> 01:30:22,918
I think we should shoot her...

1017
01:30:23,876 --> 01:30:25,335
in the head!

1018
01:30:27,710 --> 01:30:30,001
Ready. Fire!

1019
01:30:34,335 --> 01:30:35,418
It's empty!

1020
01:30:37,418 --> 01:30:38,710
It's empty!

1021
